These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, social-worker
1. the musician is in an even position##4
2. the social-worker is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | drawing | gardening |
| Job     | social-worker    | musician   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, climbing
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | sprite | tea        |
| Sport      | skateboarding  | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, rock
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, indonesian
1. the russian is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | gospel |
| Nationality   | russian | indonesian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite
There 2 different types of food: garlic, tomato
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person eating tomato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea      | sprite |
| Food       | garlic | tomato    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
