 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter
1. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | snowboarding | sailing  |
| Transport   | scooter  | skateboard |

 #################################

 
